Bugfix/incorrect movie winner

issue.title: When Wallace & Gromit: The Curse of the Were-Rabbit is the winner, it is declared as Wallace (2014)
Bugfix/multiple nominations
issue.body:
Check that a movie has not been nominated before adding it to the nominations service.

Also fix latent bug where imdb ids were not updated on updated nominations.

This led to the following sequence being able to nominate duplicates even with the previous change:

```
Alice: Nominates X with id 1
>Nomination is accepted
Bob: Nominates X with id 1
>Nomination is not accepted due to duplicate id
Alice: Changes nomination to Y with id 2
>Alices nomination changes movie name to Y but does not update id
Bob: Nominates Y with id 2
>Nomination is accepted
Bob; Nominates X with id 1
>Nomination still not accepted
```

issue.title: Feature/help command
issue.body:
Added summary, name, and remarks annotations to all existing commands.

Added help commands
!help <- prints all available modules and their summary annotations
!help <command> <- prints detailed information on a module and its commands

issue.title: Feature/style conventions
issue.body:
Changes made:

- Public members should use PascalCasing
- All methods should use PascalCasing
- // Comments should start with a space and a capital letter
- ID when camelCased or PascalCased is Id
- Added spacing for readability in certain methods
- Curly braces should be on new lines generally
- When it is obvious what a type is var should be used
